.DT
set_goal_plan_data
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_goal_plan_data

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_goal_plan_data -  This method sets the default data associated with the specified plan.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_goal_plan_data(string goal,
string plan,
mixed data)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^goal%^RESET%^ - the goal to check the data for
%^BOLD%^plan%^RESET%^ - the name of the plan
%^BOLD%^data%^RESET%^ - the data associated with the plan
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/goals_inherit.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the default data associated with the specified plan.
This should be things like global plan things, the level at which the
npc will run away.  Etc.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_default_plan_data()

.EP

